version_description:
•Added Today’s Matches
•General enhancements of the fancy variety
•Additions to the registration flow to make it fast and not-at-all furious

You asked and we listened...added by popular demand:
- Updated UI for ease of use
- Import Photos from Facebook
- Fixed a few bugs

Thanks for giving us feedback, we updated and improved the matches in Are You Interested.

Give us a shout out to let us know what you think.
Squashed bugs to improve app load times & uploading photos through Facebook
Performance Enhancements
Bug Fixes!
